AUDIO: 'and it shows you the input audio right alongside the cloned output. So, here\'s the input audio, a real voice sample. Some call me nature. Others call me Mother Nature. Now listen to the output. I don\'t really care what'

[01:18] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'you call me. I\'ve been a silent spectator, watching species evolve, empires rise and fall. Yeah, that cloning is clean, the tone matches, and here\'s something subtle but'

