AUDIO: 'and lovely animals everywhere. Every combination produces a distinct result, and it\'s a genuinely flexible system. On top of that, there\'s fine-grained emotional control through inline tags. You drop a laughter tag, a sigh tag, or'

[04:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'a surprise tag directly into your text, and the model interprets them contextually. I\'ll show you exactly how that behaves when we get into our own testing. All right, let\'s get into the actual model. First stop, the Hugging Face'

