VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'gigs. That is genuinely lightweight for what it delivers. For local use, you need at least 4 GB of VRAM for shorter outputs, and at least 8 GB if you\'re generating longer text. And yes, MacBook users, you can run this locally, too.'

[05:36] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Same goes for Windows or Linux with an Nvidia GPU. But the easiest path in is the free Google Colab notebook. Head to my GitHub repo, I regularly add notebooks there for you, and you\'ll see'

